An aging Spencer Tracy and a young Robert Wagner, Richard Widmark. Classic western action with just a bit of social commentary (don&amp;#039;t worry, it doesn&amp;#039;t get in the way of the movie).  Obviously one of my favorites or it wouldn&amp;#039;t be here.  I like this on just about every level.


Wide screen, color, dvd rip, English and Spanish audio tracks, the English is a little soft with headphones from the computer but ok with the amp&amp;#039;d speakers, good quality on the video.

